## ğŸ§ª API Endpoints

### ğŸ” Auth
```http
POST   /api/auth/register
POST   /api/auth/login
```

### ğŸ› Products
```http
GET    /api/products?page=1&limit=5&search=shoes&category=electronics
POST   /api/products           (admin only)
```

### ğŸ§º Cart (customer only)
```http
GET    /api/cart
POST   /api/cart/add
PUT    /api/cart/update
DELETE /api/cart/remove
```

### ğŸ“¦ Orders (customer only)
```http
POST   /api/orders/place
GET    /api/orders/my
```

